(42, 14, 24, 58, 12, 25, 26, 'none of those men which were bidden', 'Invitation and Rejection Theme', 'This connection highlights the theme of rejection of a divine invitation. Both passages emphasize the consequences of refusing the call, whether from earthly or heavenly sources.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
